description: What do you get when you combine the classic American hot dog with the unique flavors of Asia? —Dojo Dog! Don't settle for the ordinary. Add a kick to your day with Dojo Dog. Try our fusion of natural all-beef hot dogs with the finest Asian-inspired ingredients. Taste the premium 100% beef frankfurter and fresh French hoagie roll from top quality local suppliers in the Bay Area. Dojo Dogs uses an all naturally smoked, 100% gourmet beef sausage in all natural casing paired with a Premium French Bun hand made locally fresh every day!
name: Dojo Dog
